column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "893F66684D831A940A346FBC26B159DA", "Welcome. I\'ve never seen you before. Where are you from?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "D6F5368E4FF0AC8113524EAC9BAD9D37", "The city. Actually, I\'m from another world.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "932357BB4F2B0108C6B132B0D3368E61", "You understand my language?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "324B63B64904ABB1F5577EA0D7210560", "Sometimes it\'s hard and I don\'t sell much here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "388E619342B3A20B81ED71BE7CA8FFAF", "I see.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E16A03854DB3642DF9357EA24BF6F165", "Many shoppers stopped coming.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "BFA0AAE14C3C952A63ECDD9B248163A2", "It must be the trouble on the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E3EC3B504E363E746F7EE9800ADF6705", "Help me do something.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "95166DA74EE9A42B7D05F99BB03F27F9", "Can you work in my shop?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "AF6A4C9B40FEF3C623CEDA8CCA775ECA", "Your shop?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "8F9C17C241FC3E9810317B8F93CEA342", "Half day? The more you sell, the more I\'ll pay you. You know our language.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E944C5F44318DFD7A2F24F90AA6E1131", "You might lose money.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "A3399254433F28DD9BE70784E5CAD9D0", "Don\'t worry. It\'ll be good for me. How about eight hours?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "B1326F904E4FB61BB3C313B448004223", "That\'s too bad. Come back when you have time.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "AD872BCA40A1C4A15BD66888B911612B", "You want to work?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "27E02E4140AC9D37914C2E98E3550C19", "Well, it\'s half way done.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "347B3346459F00FDFD1C369C49410900", "The way it\'s going, we won\'t make any money. Try harder.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E080879D41B853D4919266AF6D568C99", "The sales are good. We can make some money.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "F24292754CACC6C0500CD5B576E7F736", "I haven\'t had this much business in a long time. Keep it up!")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "735023354288CEEF8BA2DCB97BE05334", "I think it\'s time. Thank you for your work.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "BB9B3BAE446F7FE911614C8F582E913F", "It could have been better, but it wasn\'t that bad. Don\'t give up.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "4BC453034468B8B61A2B3DAB6A86D7DC", "You can do better. I want you to work more.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "0EE062A94D56367F9CC93A895D05E921", "Your wisdom, character and guts are what we need to save this island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "6480849842F9F60B28167AADF6D87C6B", "What are you talking about?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E842594840FB4A4E160036AC165F0239", "I was testing you to see if you are capable of saving us.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "647D0B7B4B206877B40769A6841FE26A", "It\'s important to be good in battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "7E281B51474A4819CA08FD9BBD9969AC", "Besides power, courage and wisdom are also needed.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "A0EE4A7646F3439FA8BAFA87222B2767", "Did we pass the test?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "E12BED1E40A71A46FF2F12A94ACC0173", "Yes, I\'ll help you as much as I can.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "313DD35D4476DCCBBB5D9B9D000B0986", "Will you come to the city? What will you do with the shop?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "18794D3146FB74754B00D48F471481EF", "I can open a shop later. This shop\'s duty is done.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C5520E6F4242CFCA7055CF8204360200]", "3553771241B862AB94409DA4B513A897", "Monochromon joins the city!")
